{"tid":1394841,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[提醒] 狗屋可圍不可攻","createTime":"2019-08-01T14:23:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T14:26:21.000Z","uid":89320,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c77cb9d3f93159f040e2d66f5d77c8625490cbe9","tid":1394841,"uid":89320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:23:59.000Z","msg":"代朋友出<br />\n<br />\n見呢輪圍狗屋嘅情況頻密咗<br />\n用膝頭哥諗都知班狗一定會諗辦法搞9夢遊人士<br />\n所以特登出post講一講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信好多夢遊落街嘅都係醒字派 自有分數<br />\n不過長氣啲講<br />\n現場情況一混亂 真係好容易衝動咗<br />\n唔想兄弟出事 狗屋只可圍不可攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家萬事小心<br />\n<br />\n最後煩膠港女想提大家<br />\n班黑狗係要屌 要清算<br />\n但避免錯foc落警民衝突度<br />\n我地抗爭既同時都記得原本既訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4156883b53210bd902005af79f74513f9339e50","tid":1394841,"uid":296509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:26:21.000Z","msg":"久唔久圍一次，齊打消耗戰"}]}